data.description: Come take a look at this beautiful country home, surrounded by all the wildlife and foliage our area has to offer while still being a part of a neighborhood. This house is nicely secluded through its own private path from the quickly growing Avis/Spring Hill neighborhoods. The house offers a warm welcome when you walk into the first sitting area through the main entrance. Throughout the house, you can expect plenty of storage space with a spacious closet in every bedroom, lots of cabinetry in the kitchen, and a secondary entrance through the mudroom/utility room. Enjoy dinner with a view, as the dining room looks out through a double glass door onto the beautiful hills of our area. The main living room includes a large fireplace in the corner of the room with gas hookup capabilities. Enjoy additional storage outside in the large 10x12 shed.
